# Testing Conventions — iframe-app

- Vitest + React Testing Library. No Jest.
- Mock Nominatim with `msw`, not by stubbing `fetch` directly.
- The RPC bridge's pure logic (`dispatchRpcRequest`, `isTrustedParentMessage`,
  origin checks) lives in `src/lib/rpc-bridge.ts` specifically so it can be
  unit tested with plain mock objects, with no React and no real
  `postMessage` involved — keep it that way; don't move dispatch logic into
  the `useRpcBridge` hook itself.
- One behavior per `it(...)` block.
- Hooks are tested with `renderHook`, wrapped in a `QueryClientProvider`
  test helper — see `src/test/` for the shared wrapper.
